# CAS Reader V2 — Phase R-Sprint (Mock-Dispatcher + Schema-Validator)
# Spec: docs/CAS_READER_PROMPT_V2_SPEC.md
# Phase R3: Mock-Implementation für Tests, KEIN Live-PDF-Read.
